Dialogue: 0.0:00:51.40.0:00:55.35.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}(FOOTSTEPS CRUNCHING)
Dialogue: 0.0:00:58.07.0:00:59.57.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}(WIND HOWLING)
Dialogue: 0.0:01:25.80.0:01:28.80.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}(SPEAKING ARABIC)
Dialogue: 0.0:01:45.91.0:01:47.63.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}(IN ARABIC)\NIt's almost new.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:50.08.0:01:52.34.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(IN ARABIC)\NThree hundred cartridges.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:55.67.0:01:57.68.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}The guy who\Ngave it to me said...
Dialogue: 0.0:01:57.67.0:02:03.47.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}you can hit\Nas far as three kilometers.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:10.01.0:02:12.01.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}How much are you asking\Nfor all of this?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:12.02.0:02:14.03.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}One thousand dirhams.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:14.02.0:02:15.98.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}One thousand dirhams?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:19.99.0:02:22.49.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(332.432)}I'll give you\Nfive hundred.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:27.08.0:02:28.08.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(332.432)}And a goat.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:37.21.0:02:42.76.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}With this rifle. your sons\Nwill kill plenty of jackals.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:47.93.0:02:50.22.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.432)}Here. let one\Nof your boys try.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:50.22.0:02:51.94.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.432)}Let Yussef shoot.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:51.94.0:02:54.44.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}AHMED:\NDad. I want to shoot first.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:02.53.0:03:05.78.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}This is the safety.\NPush it in when you're ready.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:08.40.0:03:09.65.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}(CHUCKLING)
Dialogue: 0.0:03:09.66.0:03:12.05.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}If he doesn't\Nhit the jackals.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:12.04.0:03:13.66.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}at least he'll scare\Nthe shit out of them.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:13.66.0:03:14.96.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.432)}Your turn Yussef.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:18.05.0:03:19.55.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}(RIFLE COCKING)
Dialogue: 0.0:03:29.18.0:03:31.35.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}He shoots better than you.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:39.40.0:03:41.24.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}YASIRA: Good luck.\Nhave a good day.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:41.24.0:03:42.15.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}God bless you.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:42.16.0:03:46.28.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(345.432)}Kill at least\Nthree jackals.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:46.28.0:03:50.67.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}HASSAN: Make sure no one\Nsees you with the rifle...
Dialogue: 0.0:03:50.66.0:03:54.67.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}if you see\Nsomeone coming. hide it.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:57.00.0:03:58.92.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}(BABY CRYING)
Dialogue: 0.0:04:14.85.0:04:16.60.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}(GOAT BLEATING)
Dialogue: 0.0:04:17.89.0:04:19.02.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(332.432)}Yussef!
Dialogue: 0.0:04:26.07.0:04:27.38.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.432)}Yussef!
Dialogue: 0.0:04:29.95.0:04:32.40.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Yussef! Yussef!
Dialogue: 0.0:04:33.91.0:04:35.32.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:37.13.0:04:39.13.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}I told you.\Ndon't spy on her.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:39.13.0:04:40.83.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.432)}What do you care?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:40.83.0:04:42.33.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}Move it.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:02.52.0:05:03.52.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}(METAL CLINKING)
Dialogue: 0.0:05:03.52.0:05:05.52.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}AHMED: Five to two.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:07.52.0:05:08.57.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(332.432)}YUSSEF: There's\Na jackal.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:08.57.0:05:09.99.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}Where?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:10.49.0:05:11.49.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}Over there.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:16.62.0:05:18.68.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}YUSSEF: What are you doing.\Nyou idiot?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:37.30.0:05:39.14.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}Zohra doesn't mind.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:40.11.0:05:42.62.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}She doesn't. but I do.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:44.61.0:05:49.11.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(332.432)}This is between\Nher and me.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:49.12.0:05:54.13.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}You're both pigs.\NNext time\NI'm going to tell Dad.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:54.12.0:05:55.87.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.432)}Stay out of this.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:55.87.0:05:59.57.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}If you want me\Nto stay out of it.\Ndon't do it.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:52.21.0:06:53.71.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}(GUN FIRING)
Dialogue: 0.0:07:00.05.0:07:02.02.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}YUSSEF: What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0.0:07:02.36.0:07:03.78.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}(GUN COCKING)
Dialogue: 0.0:07:03.77.0:07:06.89.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Hassan said this bullet\Ncould reach three kilometers.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:07.39.0:07:08.89.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}That rock didn't move.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:09.40.0:07:11.79.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}You don't know\Nhow to shoot.\NGive me the rifle.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:20.04.0:07:20.99.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}See.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:21.37.0:07:23.62.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Yeah. but that's not\Nthree kilometers.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:37.14.0:07:39.51.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}I bet the bullet\Ncan't hit that far.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:43.60.0:07:45.61.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}These bullets are lame.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:46.23.0:07:47.73.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}You're not aiming right.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:51.07.0:07:53.65.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}What'll you give me\Nif I hit that car?
Dialogue: 0.0:07:54.61.0:07:56.11.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}AHMED: I'll shoot.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:02.58.0:08:04.58.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}You see? Nothing.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:04.58.0:08:05.58.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Let me shoot.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:08.04.0:08:09.92.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}Shoot at it.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:24.39.0:08:26.69.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}AHMED: See... nothing.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:28.52.0:08:30.78.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}You're right.\Nthey're useless.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:52.63.0:08:55.80.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}AMELIA: (IN SPANISH)\NWhere are these kids?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:55.80.0:08:59.00.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:59.00.0:09:01.34.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}I'm coming to get you...
Dialogue: 0.0:09:01.34.0:09:02.76.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(358.432)}DEBBIE: Base!
Dialogue: 0.0:09:03.26.0:09:04.76.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}(PHONE RINGING)
Dialogue: 0.0:09:04.76.0:09:06.76.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(332.432)}You win.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:07.26.0:09:08.98.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.408)}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hYes?\N{\i1}RICHARD: Amelia?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:08.98.0:09:10.48.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(410.432)}Yes. sir.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:10.98.0:09:12.48.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}Hi. How's everything?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:12.49.0:09:15.00.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}Everything is okay. sir.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:14.99.0:09:16.49.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}Mrs. Rachel told me.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:16.49.0:09:17.99.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}I am very sorry. sir.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:18.82.0:09:20.24.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.432)}How's Mrs. Susan?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:20.24.0:09:22.16.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}She's better now.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:22.16.0:09:24.66.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}They're going to\Nhave to operate. but...
Dialogue: 0.0:09:24.66.0:09:27.67.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}Look. Rachel's\Nflying in tonight.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:27.67.0:09:30.67.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}She's gonna find someone\Nto take care of the kids\Nso you can go.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:30.67.0:09:32.67.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}Thank you. sir. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:32.67.0:09:34.67.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}I really appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:34.67.0:09:37.17.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}So. look after them. okay?\NDon't tell them anything.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:37.18.0:09:39.69.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}No. no. no. Don't worry. sir.\NDon't worry. Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:39.68.0:09:40.68.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}Put Mike on. please.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:40.68.0:09:42.18.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}Yes. sir.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:42.18.0:09:44.13.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Mike? Your dad is calling.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:47.89.0:09:50.39.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.408)}\h\h\h\h\h\hHi. Daddy.\N{\i1}Hi. sweetie. How are you?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:50.39.0:09:54.39.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}Good. Dad. guess what?\NToday they brought\Nhermit crabs to class.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:54.89.0:09:56.39.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}Oh. really?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:56.40.0:09:58.91.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}I held one in my hands.\NIt bit me.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:58.90.0:10:01.40.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}It really\Ndidn't bleed. but...
Dialogue: 0.0:10:01.90.0:10:03.70.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}Dad? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:04.20.0:10:05.95.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}I'm okay. Everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:06.46.0:10:07.47.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}Mariana wanted\Nto take one home.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:07.46.0:10:08.82.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}But the teacher\Ndidn't let her. She was...
Dialogue: 0.0:10:09.33.0:10:10.84.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I don't want to go to sleep.\NI don't want to go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:11.33.0:10:13.46.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(345.432)}Mike. Mike.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:13.46.0:10:15.75.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(358.432)}(IN SPANISH)\NDid you brush\Nyour teeth?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:21.75.0:10:22.75.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(397.432)}(CHUCKLES)
Dialogue: 0.0:10:26.26.0:10:28.76.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}Sleep with angels.\Nmy darling.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:30.76.0:10:32.26.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}Sleep well.\Nsweetie.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:40.11.0:10:41.12.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}DEBBIE: Amelia?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:44.11.0:10:45.61.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Amelia?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:50.28.0:10:51.78.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}Could you leave\Nthe light on?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:51.78.0:10:53.53.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.432)}(IN SPANISH)\NYou are already\Nsharing a room...
Dialogue: 0.0:10:53.54.0:10:56.85.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}didn't we agree to sleep\Nwith the lights off?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:56.84.0:10:58.21.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}But I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:58.71.0:11:00.68.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}There's nothing\Nto be scared of.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:00.68.0:11:02.63.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}But I'm scared\Nthat what happened to Sam
Dialogue: 0.0:11:02.63.0:11:05.13.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}is going to\Nhappen to me.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:06.35.0:11:10.02.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}No. that won't\Nhappen to you.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:11.10.0:11:13.35.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}Sam died while\Nhe was sleeping.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:13.36.0:11:15.37.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}No. baby. no. no.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:15.36.0:11:17.14.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}That only\Nhappens to some babies
Dialogue: 0.0:11:17.14.0:11:20.64.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}when they're really.\Nreally little.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:20.65.0:11:23.82.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}Your brother is already\Nhigh in heaven. baby.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:24.82.0:11:26.32.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}I'll sit here with you.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:26.32.0:11:28.70.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}But you can't\Ntalk anymore. okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:11:29.71.0:11:30.83.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(358.432)}Go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:39.42.0:11:41.39.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}(SHUSHING)
Dialogue: 0.0:11:48.64.0:11:49.64.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}(PHONE RINGING)
Dialogue: 0.0:11:53.51.0:11:55.76.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}(PHONE RINGING)
Dialogue: 0.0:12:02.10.0:12:04.07.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}But today is my\Nson's wedding. sir.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:04.57.0:12:06.07.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}RICHARD:\NCancel your son's wedding.\NI'll pay for another one.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:06.08.0:12:09.59.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}I'll pay for a better one.\NI need you to do this. Amelia.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:09.58.0:12:12.58.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}Everything is ready. sir.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:12.58.0:12:16.08.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}Can't anyone come\Nto take care of the kids?\NIt's just one day. sir.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:16.09.0:12:18.10.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}How do you expect\Nme to find someone\Nfrom here?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:18.09.0:12:20.59.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}Susan's still recovering.\Nand Rachel can't make it\Nto take care of the kids.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:20.59.0:12:22.37.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}Can't do it. Hold on.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:23.88.0:12:25.89.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}We're really\Ncounting on you. Amelia.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:25.88.0:12:27.38.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}I'm sorry.\Nbut you have to do this.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:27.88.0:12:28.88.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.408)}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hBut...\N{\i1}Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:28.88.0:12:29.88.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}{\i1}(PHONE CLICKS)
Dialogue: 0.0:12:38.97.0:12:41.64.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}AMELIA: (IN SPANISH)\NHow can I be\Nin two places at once?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:41.64.0:12:45.28.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}I'm just asking you\Nto take them for today.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:45.78.0:12:48.28.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}WOMAN ON PHONE: I can't.\Nthe mister is still home.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:48.28.0:12:49.78.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(332.432)}And they aren't\Ngoing out?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:49.79.0:12:51.30.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}No. I don't\Nthink so.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:53.37.0:12:56.62.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(332.432)}Okay. I'll talk\Nto you later.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:01.46.0:13:02.46.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(332.432)}LUCIA:\NI can't Amelia.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:02.97.0:13:04.98.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}AMELIA: Please.\Nit's my son's wedding.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:04.97.0:13:08.80.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Just for the day. Lucia.\NI'll be back\Nfor them tonight.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:08.80.0:13:11.89.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}And what do I say\Nto Mrs. Catherine?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:11.89.0:13:15.89.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I don't know. Tell her\Nthey're your nephews.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:15.89.0:13:17.93.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}Right. because they look\Nso much like me...
Dialogue: 0.0:13:17.93.0:13:19.73.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(137.432)}with my American looking face!
Dialogue: 0.0:13:21.57.0:13:23.07.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}DEBBIE: Are we going to\Nsee your house?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:23.07.0:13:26.07.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Yes. You are\Ngoing to see my house.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:26.07.0:13:28.07.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(371.432)}Is it far?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:28.07.0:13:30.07.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}No. no.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:30.08.0:13:31.84.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}(SPEAKING SPANISH)
Dialogue: 0.0:13:33.20.0:13:37.21.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}{\i1}(SPANISH SONG PLAYING)
Dialogue: 0.0:13:43.34.0:13:44.34.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}SANTIAGO: (IN SPANISH)\NWhat's up?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:44.34.0:13:45.34.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}(CHATTERING\NIN SPANISH)
Dialogue: 0.0:13:45.34.0:13:46.84.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(397.432)}Hi Auntie.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:46.84.0:13:49.34.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}Great to see you.\NSantiago.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:49.35.0:13:51.36.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(137.432)}(AMELIA CHATTERING IN SPANISH)
Dialogue: 0.0:13:51.35.0:13:52.85.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}Mike. Debbie.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:52.85.0:13:53.85.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(384.432)}Hello!
Dialogue: 0.0:13:54.35.0:13:55.85.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}Hello. hello.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:55.85.0:13:57.85.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}(IN SPANISH)\NThey're really shy.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:57.85.0:13:59.85.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}(IN SPANISH)\NWhat? These kids\Nare coming with us?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:59.86.0:14:02.37.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I couldn't find\Nanyone to watch them.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:02.36.0:14:03.89.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Their parents\Nwon't return tonight.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:03.89.0:14:05.89.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}Why bring them?\NThey'll drive you crazy.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:05.89.0:14:08.90.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Don't worry.\Nthey're very good kids.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:08.90.0:14:11.73.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(345.432)}Don't you want\Nto leave them\Nwith somebody?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:11.73.0:14:13.23.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}I know a girl who\Ncan take care of them.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:13.24.0:14:15.75.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Are you crazy?\NI have to take them\Nwith me.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:15.74.0:14:18.16.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I can't leave them\Nwith just anybody.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:19.66.0:14:20.66.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Are you sure. Auntie?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:20.66.0:14:23.16.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(384.432)}(REPLIES\NIN SPANISH)
Dialogue: 0.0:14:23.16.0:14:27.16.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}{\i1}(SPANISH SONG BLARING)
Dialogue: 0.0:14:37.59.0:14:39.06.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}(GREETING IN ARABIC)
Dialogue: 0.0:14:39.06.0:14:41.73.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}(IN FRENCH-ACCENTED ENGLISH)\NYou want to order?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:41.73.0:14:46.02.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}Yeah. I'll have\Nthe chicken couscous\Nand a Coke.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:47.90.0:14:49.94.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}What do you have\Nthat doesn't have fat in it?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:49.94.0:14:52.57.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Everything is delicious.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:52.57.0:14:55.58.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I'll have the fried eggplant\Nand a Diet Coke.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:55.58.0:14:57.58.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}WAITER: Sorry.\Nwe don't have Diet Coke.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:57.58.0:14:58.58.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Then a regular Coke.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:58.58.0:15:00.00.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(358.432)}Two Cokes.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:16.68.0:15:18.68.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}Richard.\Nwhy did we come here?
Dialogue: 0.0:15:22.81.0:15:24.11.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}What do you mean. why?
Dialogue: 0.0:15:24.11.0:15:27.62.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Really.\NWhy are we here?
Dialogue: 0.0:15:33.62.0:15:35.13.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}To be alone.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:39.49.0:15:40.87.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}SUSAN: "Alone."
Dialogue: 0.0:15:53.67.0:15:54.67.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Throw out the ice.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:55.17.0:15:56.50.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(332.432)}The Coke's hot.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:56.51.0:15:59.43.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Yeah. but you don't know\Nwhat kind of water\Nis in there.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:02.68.0:16:05.73.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}(WATER SPLASHING)
Dialogue: 0.0:16:12.07.0:16:14.57.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}Jesus Christ.\NWhy can't you just relax?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:14.57.0:16:16.41.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}Why are you\Nso stressed?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:16.41.0:16:18.33.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}You are the reason\NI'm stressed.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:18.33.0:16:19.83.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}You're the reason\Nwhy I can't relax.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:20.33.0:16:21.83.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}You could if you tried.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:25.87.0:16:27.87.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}You don't think I tried?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:36.46.0:16:38.96.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.432)}You're never\Ngonna forgive me.\Nare you?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:49.73.0:16:52.24.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}You know what\NI'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:54.15.0:16:56.16.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}Hey. I'm not\Ngonna argue.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:04.96.0:17:05.96.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:08.46.0:17:11.46.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}You just let me know\Nwhen you're ready to argue.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:12.97.0:17:14.98.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}If you're not\Ngonna run away again.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:12.83.0:19:14.17.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}(GLASS CLINKING)
Dialogue: 0.0:19:14.17.0:19:15.00.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}(GASPS)
Dialogue: 0.0:19:16.09.0:19:17.70.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Honey? What happened?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:17.71.0:19:18.60.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:18.59.0:19:20.09.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(ALARMED) Honey.\Nwhat happened?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:20.09.0:19:21.59.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}What happened?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:22.59.0:19:24.71.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}You're bleeding.\Nyou're bleeding.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:25.63.0:19:27.43.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.408)}Oh. my God!\NShe's been shot!
Dialogue: 0.0:19:27.43.0:19:29.18.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Jesus.\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:29.18.0:19:32.19.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.144)}(PEOPLE CHATTERING EXCITEDLY)\NYou're bleeding.\NOh. my God!
Dialogue: 0.0:19:32.19.0:19:33.47.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}(GRUNTS)
Dialogue: 0.0:19:33.47.0:19:35.19.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}RICHARD: Stop the bus!
Dialogue: 0.0:19:35.19.0:19:37.11.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}(PASSENGERS CHATTERING)
Dialogue: 0.0:19:37.11.0:19:38.61.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.408)}\h\h\hMAN: What happened?\NStop the bus!
Dialogue: 0.0:19:43.28.0:19:44.73.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}(WHISTLE BLOWING)
Dialogue: 0.0:19:45.62.0:19:47.12.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}(PEOPLE CHATTERING)
Dialogue: 0.0:19:48.95.0:19:50.57.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}(WHISTLE BLOWING)
Dialogue: 0.0:20:05.72.0:20:07.30.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}(WHISTLE BLOWS)
Dialogue: 0.0:20:08.22.0:20:10.22.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}(AUDIENCE CHEERING)
Dialogue: 0.0:20:10.23.0:20:12.57.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}(CHANTING)
Dialogue: 0.0:20:16.40.0:20:17.06.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}(SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY)
Dialogue: 0.0:20:17.07.0:20:19.19.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}(IN JAPANESE)\NThe ball was out.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:19.18.0:20:22.15.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}(CHATTERING IN JAPANESE)
Dialogue: 0.0:20:23.69.0:20:25.02.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}That was out.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:25.02.0:20:26.82.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}No. it was good.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:26.83.0:20:28.50.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}That was out.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:31.45.0:20:33.25.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}I'm deaf. not blind.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:34.58.0:20:35.62.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}You're out.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:42.84.0:20:44.17.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}(WHISTLE BLOWING)
Dialogue: 0.0:20:45.63.0:20:47.63.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}(SHOWERS RUNNING)
Dialogue: 0.0:20:54.85.0:21:00.44.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}You shouldn't have\Nlost your temper.\NWe lost the game.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:00.44.0:21:04.14.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}It wasn't my fault.\Nit was the ref.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:04.15.0:21:08.46.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(137.432)}(IN JAPANESE)\NIf you hadn't been thrown out.\Nwe would've won the game.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:11.40.0:21:14.54.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}Why are you\Nin a bad mood?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:14.87.0:21:19.29.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}She's always in a bad mood\Nbecause nobody's\Nfucked her yet.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:19.29.0:21:22.30.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}I'm gonna fuck your dad\Nto get rid of my mood.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:22.30.0:21:23.71.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}(LAUGHS ALOUD)
Dialogue: 0.0:21:30.92.0:21:32.42.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I'll see you at the J-Pop.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:50.11.0:21:52.61.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(IN JAPANESE)\NWhat do you want to eat?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:54.03.0:21:58.12.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}I said I'd meet my friends\Nfrom the team at J-Pop.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:58.62.0:22:01.95.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Didn't you tell me\Nwe would have lunch together?
Dialogue: 0.0:22:01.95.0:22:04.87.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}Dad. I told you I was\Ngoing to eat with them.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:04.87.0:22:07.67.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}You never pay\Nattention to me.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:17.47.0:22:20.97.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}My mother always\Npaid attention to me.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:25.98.0:22:29.90.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Why do you want to fight?
Dialogue: 0.0:22:35.15.0:22:40.96.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I miss your mother too.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:47.83.0:22:51.00.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I'm doing the best I can.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:09.27.0:23:11.77.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Don't forget\Nthe dentist at three.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:17.41.0:23:18.78.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}Take care.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:37.27.0:23:42.56.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}(TECHNO DANCE MUSIC BLARING)
Dialogue: 0.0:23:48.28.0:23:49.73.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}(SPEAKING JAPANESE)
Dialogue: 0.0:23:52.90.0:23:54.20.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}Do you have a table?
Dialogue: 0.0:24:07.05.0:24:09.67.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(332.432)}Why all the way\Nin the corner?
Dialogue: 0.0:24:12.63.0:24:14.63.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}Isn't the view nice?
Dialogue: 0.0:24:29.85.0:24:31.65.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Do you like him?
Dialogue: 0.0:24:37.99.0:24:41.83.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}(CHATTERING IN JAPANESE)
Dialogue: 0.0:24:53.71.0:24:55.51.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}(EXCLAIMING IN TRIUMPH)
Dialogue: 0.0:25:06.27.0:25:07.77.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(IN JAPANESE)\NHello.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:12.53.0:25:13.86.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}Hello.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:19.95.0:25:21.45.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}Can I play with you?
Dialogue: 0.0:25:22.95.0:25:24.96.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}Or you can have\Na drink with us?
Dialogue: 0.0:25:27.49.0:25:29.99.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}Tell him\Nto speak slowly.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:29.99.0:25:33.08.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}Can you say that\Na little slower?
Dialogue: 0.0:25:43.06.0:25:44.42.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(332.432)}(LAUGHING)
Dialogue: 0.0:25:47.26.0:25:50.06.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}You assholes.\Nhow embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:02.03.0:26:04.03.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}(TOILET FLUSHING)
Dialogue: 0.0:26:10.79.0:26:11.80.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0.0:26:13.71.0:26:16.97.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}They look at us\Nlike we're monsters.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:16.96.0:26:18.46.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}Oh. come off it.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:33.78.0:26:35.29.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0.0:26:35.28.0:26:38.48.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Now they're going to meet\Nthe real hairy monster.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:39.48.0:26:44.03.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}(JAPANESE POP MUSIC BLARING)
Dialogue: 0.0:27:28.16.0:27:29.53.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}(LAUGHING)
Dialogue: 0.0:27:34.92.0:27:37.79.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}Don't forget your appointment\Nwith the dentist. Papa.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:37.79.0:27:39.62.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(358.432)}I have to go.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:39.62.0:27:41.54.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}I'll see you at\Nyour place. then.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:23.00.0:28:25.00.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}(IN ARABIC)\NWhat are you\Ndoing here?
Dialogue: 0.0:28:25.00.0:28:27.50.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(IN ARABIC)\NSomething we ate\Ngave us a stomach ache.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:27.51.0:28:29.52.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}The goats will die\Nif they don't eat.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:29.51.0:28:32.01.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}Wash your face\Nand take them out again.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:32.01.0:28:33.51.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}My stomach hurts.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:33.51.0:28:36.01.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}There are other\Nchores to do then.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:36.01.0:28:38.52.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}Move it. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:09.35.0:29:11.85.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(IN ARABIC)\NGod bless. Bye. bye.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:14.35.0:29:16.72.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Thank you.\NI'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:19.27.0:29:21.64.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}Tell your mother\Nto prepare dinner.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:40.24.0:29:42.58.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Did you kill\Nany jackals?
Dialogue: 0.0:29:42.58.0:29:45.92.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}We shot at them.\Nbut didn't hit any.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:46.42.0:29:49.89.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}You have to kill them.\NIf not. they're going\Nto eat all the goats.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:49.89.0:29:52.42.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Why did you\Ncome home late?
Dialogue: 0.0:29:52.42.0:29:55.89.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}They closed the road.\Nwe took the long way.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:57.98.0:30:02.07.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}Apparently some terrorists\Nkilled an American tourist.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:02.57.0:30:04.02.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}An American?
Dialogue: 0.0:30:04.02.0:30:06.85.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}Yes. the terrorists attacked\Na tour bus on the road.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:07.86.0:30:10.17.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}No. there aren't\Nany terrorists here.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:11.53.0:30:13.04.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}ABDULLAH: You never know.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:18.42.0:30:19.93.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}How do you know\Nthe American died?
Dialogue: 0.0:30:19.92.0:30:24.34.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}That's what they were saying.\NThe police are looking\Nfor the culprits.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:32.38.0:30:33.88.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}(GOATS BLEATING)
Dialogue: 0.0:30:50.03.0:30:53.37.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}{\i1}(MAN CHATTERING IN SPANISH\NON RADIO)
Dialogue: 0.0:31:23.68.0:31:25.85.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}You see how easy it is\Nto get into paradise?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:25.85.0:31:27.23.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}Is this Mexico?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:27.24.0:31:29.20.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}(IN SPANISH)\NYes. this is Mexico.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:29.19.0:31:32.61.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}My mom told me\Nthat Mexico is\Nreally dangerous.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:32.61.0:31:35.24.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(IN SPANISH) Yeah...\Nit's full of Mexicans.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:35.74.0:31:37.24.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}AMELIA: Don't talk\Nlike that.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:37.25.0:31:38.76.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}It's not true.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:43.53.0:31:47.45.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}SANTIAGO: (IN ENGLISH)\NI mean. yeah.\Nit's full of Mexicans. but...
Dialogue: 0.0:33:18.55.0:33:22.98.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(345.432)}(IN SPANISH)\NHow wonderful.\Nyou made it.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:23.77.0:33:25.80.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}You decided to bring them?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:25.80.0:33:27.02.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(332.432)}Hey. what's up?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:27.02.0:33:30.39.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}(ALL CHATTERING IN SPANISH)
Dialogue: 0.0:33:30.39.0:33:33.56.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}Oh. son.\Nlook how handsome.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:35.06.0:33:36.40.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}You look like\NJulio Preciado.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:36.40.0:33:40.57.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}Forget Julio Preciado.\Nhe looks like Luis Miguel.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:42.99.0:33:44.49.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}Debbie. Mike.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:44.99.0:33:46.91.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}These are the kids\NI take care of.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:46.91.0:33:48.62.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Say hi to Luis.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:50.08.0:33:51.91.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}SANTIAGO: Lucio. come here.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:51.91.0:33:54.33.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}This is Mike and Debbie.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:54.33.0:33:56.83.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}(IN ENGLISH) He's called\NLucio. He's gonna take\Ncare of you. okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:57.13.0:33:59.05.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}(IN SPANISH)\NTake them to play.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:59.05.0:34:02.00.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(332.432)}(AMELIA COAXING\NIN SPANISH)
Dialogue: 0.0:34:05.81.0:34:07.56.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}(CHATTERING IN SPANISH)
Dialogue: 0.0:34:07.56.0:34:11.56.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(IN SPANISH) Mom.\NI don't know how you did it.\Nbut it zipped up perfectly.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:11.57.0:34:13.99.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}And it's been 15 years\Nsince I wore this dress.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:13.99.0:34:15.86.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}You haven't\Nchanged a bit. Ma.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:15.85.0:34:19.61.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Working dear. hard work...\Nthat's what keeps you young.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:21.66.0:34:23.11.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}What are you\Nguys laughing about?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:23.11.0:34:24.61.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Nothing Ma.\Nnothing.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:26.11.0:34:29.08.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}(MUTTERING)
Dialogue: 0.0:34:39.93.0:34:43.85.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}I'll give a buck\Nto the first\Nwho catches a chicken.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:45.52.0:34:47.68.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}Careful with the 'huevos.'
Dialogue: 0.0:34:49.77.0:34:53.77.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}(ENCOURAGING IN SPANISH)
Dialogue: 0.0:34:56.89.0:34:58.56.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Very good. Debbie got one.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:01.53.0:35:03.03.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}Debbie's the winner.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:03.03.0:35:05.03.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}Okay. now we need\Nanother five.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:05.04.0:35:07.30.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}So we have five\Nchickens here.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:07.29.0:35:09.66.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Okay. now who's\Ngoing to help me?
Dialogue: 0.0:35:09.66.0:35:10.96.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}(ALL SHOUTING)
Dialogue: 0.0:35:10.96.0:35:13.46.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}You? Okay. come.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:13.46.0:35:15.91.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Hold it tight.\Nlike this.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:15.91.0:35:16.91.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Grab it right.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:21.30.0:35:25.81.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Everyone back up...\Ngive me some room.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:35.40.0:35:36.85.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}(CHILDREN LAUGHING)
Dialogue: 0.0:35:37.77.0:35:41.35.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(CHATTERING\NIN SPANISH)
Dialogue: 0.0:35:41.82.0:35:43.66.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}RICHARD: Someone. help!
Dialogue: 0.0:35:48.25.0:35:51.37.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}(PEOPLE CHATTERING)
Dialogue: 0.0:35:59.21.0:36:02.18.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}RICHARD: Is anybody a doctor?\NPlease. a doctor!
Dialogue: 0.0:36:08.13.0:36:09.63.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Where's the nearest hospital?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:09.63.0:36:11.43.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}It's far away.\NAbout four hours.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:11.44.0:36:13.45.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.408)}Is there anything closer?\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hThere's a clinic.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:13.44.0:36:17.02.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}But on the south.\NIn the bus it will take us\Nan hour and a half.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:17.02.0:36:18.02.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Away from Ouarzazate?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:18.03.0:36:20.54.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}Yes. It's the closest\Nthing we've got.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:22.90.0:36:24.86.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}BARTH: Get down!
Dialogue: 0.0:36:24.87.0:36:27.21.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.408)}RICHARD: Put that there.\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hMAN: Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:30.20.0:36:31.15.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(358.432)}Stop!
Dialogue: 0.0:36:31.87.0:36:33.04.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(384.432)}Stop!
Dialogue: 0.0:36:34.96.0:36:37.83.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}We need your help.\NMy wife's been injured.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:37.83.0:36:38.74.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.120)}(CHATTERING IN ARABIC)\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hI need your help.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:38.75.0:36:40.76.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(332.432)}Uh... Help.\NUh... Hospital.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:40.75.0:36:42.75.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}Help. come here.\NTell him we need his help!
Dialogue: 0.0:36:42.75.0:36:45.25.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}No. wait! Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0.0:36:45.25.0:36:47.75.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}Stop him! Stop him!
Dialogue: 0.0:37:01.24.0:37:04.25.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}Ouarzazate isn't this way.\NThey're going to\Nstart shooting at us.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:04.24.0:37:06.57.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.408)}Turn the bus around. Anwar!\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hIt hurts.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:06.57.0:37:09.69.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.408)}BARTH: Turn back.\NTurn the bus around!\N\h\h\h\hIt really hurts.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:10.95.0:37:13.01.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}We got to get\Nsomewhere closer.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:13.00.0:37:14.58.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Is there anywhere else\Nwe can take her?
Dialogue: 0.0:37:14.58.0:37:15.95.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}We can take her\Nto my town.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:16.42.0:37:17.92.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}ANWAR: It's near here.\Nand there is a doctor.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:17.92.0:37:20.17.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}We can call Erfoud\Nfor an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:21.84.0:37:23.17.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}Okay. Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:31.43.0:37:32.30.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(371.432)}(GROANS)
Dialogue: 0.0:38:42.50.0:38:45.50.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(137.432)}(PEOPLE CHATTERING ANIMATEDLY)
Dialogue: 0.0:39:08.40.0:39:10.41.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Watch her shoulder!\NWatch her shoulder!
Dialogue: 0.0:39:10.40.0:39:11.73.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(332.432)}Okay. Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:13.23.0:39:14.73.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}(GRUNTING)
Dialogue: 0.0:39:15.74.0:39:16.74.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}ANWAR: Turn this way.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:17.24.0:39:18.24.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}SUSAN: No. no.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:18.24.0:39:20.49.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Through the next door.\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:26.50.0:39:27.83.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(SPEAKING ARABIC)
Dialogue: 0.0:39:28.58.0:39:29.97.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}(SUSAN GROANING)
Dialogue: 0.0:39:33.64.0:39:35.64.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}(PANTING)
Dialogue: 0.0:39:35.64.0:39:36.64.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}We got to call an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:36.64.0:39:38.14.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I need to call my embassy.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:38.64.0:39:40.14.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}ANWAR: Okay. If you have\Nthe number of your embassy.\NI can go call.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:40.64.0:39:43.65.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.408)}\h\hSUSAN: Where are you going?\NI'll make the call. Okay.\NI got to go make a call.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:43.65.0:39:45.65.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.408)}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hPlease don't\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hleave me here alone.\NYou're going to be all right.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:45.65.0:39:47.15.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.408)}Can she help?\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hYeah. yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:47.15.0:39:48.18.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}Where are you going? Please\Ndon't leave me here alone.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:48.69.0:39:50.25.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.408)}Can she help?\N\h\h\h\h\hYes.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:50.24.0:39:51.99.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Listen. listen. It's gonna be\Nall right. I'm just gonna\Ngo make a call.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:51.99.0:39:54.82.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}Wait. wait. wait. wait.\NTell her she has to\Nkeep pressure right here.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:55.24.0:39:56.74.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}She cannot let go.\NDoes she understand?
Dialogue: 0.0:39:56.74.0:39:58.41.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}Yes.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:58.41.0:39:59.95.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}I'm just gonna make sure\Nhelp's on the way.\NI'm coming right back.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:59.95.0:40:01.91.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.408)}Please don't leave me.\N\h\hDoes she understand?
Dialogue: 0.0:40:01.92.0:40:03.93.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.408)}\h\hI'll be right back.\NRichard. no.\Ndon't leave me here.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:03.92.0:40:06.92.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.408)}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hI'll be right back.\NRichard. don't. Richard!
Dialogue: 0.0:40:07.20.0:40:10.01.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}I'll be back. sweetheart.\NJust gonna make the call.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:11.79.0:40:12.76.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}How's your wife?
Dialogue: 0.0:40:13.26.0:40:14.63.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}It's bad. I can't\Nstop the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:14.63.0:40:15.63.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}Get her out of\Nthere and let's go.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:15.63.0:40:17.30.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Where? Where do I take her?
Dialogue: 0.0:40:17.30.0:40:20.13.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}In Egypt in a town like this\Nthey slit 30 German\Ntourists' throats.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:20.13.0:40:21.68.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.408)}They might do the same to us.\N\hNo. sir. not here.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:21.69.0:40:23.48.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}What do you know?\NWe've got to get out of here\Nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:23.47.0:40:25.30.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}It's unbearably hot.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:25.31.0:40:27.28.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(137.408)}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hWe have to get\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hback for our children.\NLook. you can't leave us here.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:27.27.0:40:28.97.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.408)}What is the point\Nin our staying?\N\h\h\h\h\hIn case we need the bus!
Dialogue: 0.0:40:28.98.0:40:29.87.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}He can drop us off\Nand come back for you.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:29.86.0:40:31.14.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.408)}\h\h\h\h\hNo.\NI'll stay with you\Nif you need me.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:31.15.0:40:32.87.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Please just wait.\NLet me figure this out.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:32.86.0:40:35.87.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}We're not gonna risk\Nour lives. so hurry.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:45.63.0:40:48.42.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}(IN ARABIC)\NI need your phone.\NI will pay.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:01.89.0:41:03.68.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}(WOMAN SHOUTING IN ARABIC)
Dialogue: 0.0:41:06.68.0:41:09.68.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}(SHOOING IN ARABIC)
Dialogue: 0.0:41:14.66.0:41:17.53.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}Rachel? Rachel?\NIt's Richard. Listen.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:17.52.0:41:19.53.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}RACHEL: Hey.\Nwhere are you?
Dialogue: 0.0:41:19.53.0:41:21.03.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(332.432)}We're still...\NListen. listen.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:21.03.0:41:22.53.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}There's been an accident.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:22.53.0:41:24.53.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}Your sister's been shot.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:24.53.0:41:26.53.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}She's been shot.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:27.03.0:41:28.95.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(358.432)}I don't know.\NI... I...\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:28.95.0:41:30.45.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.408)}\h\h\h\h\h\hShe's hit in the neck.\N{\i1}Oh. my God!
Dialogue: 0.0:41:30.45.0:41:33.17.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}Listen. listen. I need you\Nto call the embassy
Dialogue: 0.0:41:33.17.0:41:34.67.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(345.432)}and tell them\Nwhat happened.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:34.68.0:41:37.69.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}And call Mark. okay?\NCall Mark.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:37.68.0:41:39.18.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0.0:41:39.18.0:41:41.01.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(358.432)}Where are we?
Dialogue: 0.0:41:41.02.0:41:44.03.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}Tazarine. Three hours\Nsouthwest of Erfoud.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:44.02.0:41:48.52.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}Tazarine.\NT-A-Z-A-R-I-N-E.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:49.52.0:41:52.19.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}Three hours\Nsouthwest of Erfoud.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:52.19.0:41:53.69.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}It's in the desert.\NIt's a village.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:53.69.0:41:55.19.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}How are we\Nsupposed to find you?
Dialogue: 0.0:41:55.70.0:41:57.32.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}Listen. listen. listen!
Dialogue: 0.0:41:57.31.0:41:58.31.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.408)}This is urgent. okay?\N{\i1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:58.32.0:41:59.83.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}Call the embassy.\NThey will help us.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:00.32.0:42:01.37.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}And call James!
Dialogue: 0.0:42:07.83.0:42:09.17.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}(GREETING IN ARABIC)
Dialogue: 0.0:42:10.63.0:42:11.63.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}This is the doctor.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:11.63.0:42:14.63.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}(GREETING IN ARABIC)
Dialogue: 0.0:42:32.85.0:42:34.10.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(345.432)}Easy.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:42.24.0:42:43.74.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}(SUSAN SHUDDERING)
Dialogue: 0.0:42:45.86.0:42:48.33.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}RICHARD: Easy. easy.\NEasy! Easy!
Dialogue: 0.0:42:48.33.0:42:49.83.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}I can't. I can't.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:51.84.0:42:53.85.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}RICHARD: Tell him. easy.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:53.84.0:42:56.51.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}DOCTOR: (IN ARABIC)\NThe bullet didn't\Ntouch her spine.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:56.51.0:43:01.01.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}If she stays like this.\Nshe will bleed to death.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:01.01.0:43:02.21.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}What did he say?
Dialogue: 0.0:43:02.21.0:43:03.55.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(358.432)}He says
Dialogue: 0.0:43:04.52.0:43:05.52.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}she will be fine.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:05.52.0:43:07.64.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Don't you fucking lie to me.\NYou tell me what he said.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:07.63.0:43:09.13.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}Tell me what he said!
Dialogue: 0.0:43:09.14.0:43:10.81.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}(SPEAKING ARABIC)
Dialogue: 0.0:43:11.31.0:43:13.12.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}Hospital. Hospital.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:13.11.0:43:14.64.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I know. hospital!\NWhat can you do?
Dialogue: 0.0:43:14.64.0:43:16.53.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}ANWAR: (IN ARABIC)\NIs there anything\Nwe can do?
Dialogue: 0.0:43:16.53.0:43:18.53.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}I have to\Nstitch up the wound\Nto stop the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:18.53.0:43:21.40.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(IN ENGLISH)\NHe says he need\Nto sew up the wounds.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:21.40.0:43:22.70.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}SUSAN: What did he say?
Dialogue: 0.0:43:25.45.0:43:27.79.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}He said you need\Nsome stitches. honey.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:29.62.0:43:32.66.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}Stitches?\NWhat do you mean.\Nstitches?
Dialogue: 0.0:43:32.66.0:43:33.79.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}(WHISPERING) What kind\Nof doctor is he?
Dialogue: 0.0:43:33.79.0:43:36.05.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}He's a veterinarian.\NBut he is good.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:36.05.0:43:38.30.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}DOCTOR: (IN ARABIC)\NAnd tell him\Nher clavicle is broken.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:38.30.0:43:41.80.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}He says she has a broken bone\Nand he has to\Nput a splint on it.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:41.80.0:43:45.72.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}If he doesn't\Nsew up her wound.\Nshe might bleed to death.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:45.72.0:43:47.59.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.408)}\h\h\hWait. Wait. wait.\NSUSAN: Richard.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:50.06.0:43:51.06.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}No. no. no. Richard.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:51.06.0:43:53.01.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}DOCTOR: We have to\Nhold her down.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:53.01.0:43:56.90.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.408)}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hRichard. Richard.\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hNo. no. no. no.\NWait. Wait. Wait. Wait.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:02.91.0:44:07.08.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.408)}\hRichard. don't let him.\NHoney. we have to do this.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:07.08.0:44:09.53.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}It's still bleeding.\NWe got to stop the bleeding.\NYou gotta do this.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:10.03.0:44:11.45.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.408)}\h\h\hWe have to do this.\NNo. no. don't let him.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:11.45.0:44:12.78.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.408)}\h\hListen to me.\NNo. no. no. please.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:12.78.0:44:14.78.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}No. no. no. no.\NRichard. don't.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:14.79.0:44:16.60.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}(GROANS)
Dialogue: 0.0:44:16.59.0:44:18.20.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.408)}\h\h\h\h\hNo!\NYou got to be still.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:18.21.0:44:22.13.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.408)}Richard. don't let him! No.\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\hYou got to be still.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:22.13.0:44:24.35.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}RICHARD: Be strong.\Nbe strong. Shh.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:24.34.0:44:27.71.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}(SUSAN SCREAMING)
Dialogue: 0.0:44:28.18.0:44:31.30.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(384.432)}(INAUDIBLE)
Dialogue: 0.0:44:46.73.0:44:47.70.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(SPEAKING JAPANESE)
Dialogue: 0.0:44:48.20.0:44:49.20.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}(TELEPHONE RINGING)
Dialogue: 0.0:44:51.62.0:44:53.12.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(137.432)}FEMALE ASSISTANT: Here\Nare the sterilized drill bits.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:53.12.0:44:54.37.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:57.08.0:44:59.16.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}You have cavities\Nin two molars.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:24.32.0:45:25.82.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0.0:45:36.75.0:45:38.58.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0.0:45:49.88.0:45:51.13.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Get out.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:56.35.0:45:58.02.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}Get out right now.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:37.48.0:46:39.48.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}Yes. I'll let him know.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:42.65.0:46:44.90.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}That's Mr. Wataya's\Ndaughter.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:45.85.0:46:46.85.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:51.44.0:46:54.78.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Are you Yasujiro\NWataya's daughter?
Dialogue: 0.0:46:54.78.0:46:57.78.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(371.432)}She's\Ndeaf-mute...
Dialogue: 0.0:46:57.78.0:47:02.17.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}Face her when you speak\Nso she can read your lips.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:05.84.0:47:07.96.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Are you Yasujiro\NWataya's daughter?
Dialogue: 0.0:47:10.43.0:47:15.76.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}We are Yoshjo Hamano\Nand Kenji Mamiya of\Nthe Metropolitan Police.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:18.69.0:47:21.20.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}We would like\Nto see your father.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:33.65.0:47:40.62.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}No. it's nothing bad.\NWe just want to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:40.62.0:47:42.62.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Do you know\Nwhere he is?
Dialogue: 0.0:47:45.13.0:47:48.91.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Please tell him to call.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:50.92.0:47:55.09.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Don't be scared.\NWe just want to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:58.89.0:47:59.73.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:10.10.0:48:13.61.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}{\i1}Chieko. I waited for you.\NI have a meeting so\NI'll be back late.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:13.61.0:48:15.61.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}I left you a bento box. Papa.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:21.87.0:48:25.93.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(345.432)}{\i1}I'm on my way\Nto your place.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:26.70.0:48:28.70.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0.0:48:31.63.0:48:33.39.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0.0:48:39.77.0:48:41.55.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}{\i1}(SPEAKING JAPANESE)
Dialogue: 0.0:48:43.77.0:48:47.31.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.96)}{\i1}(NARRATOR CHATTERING ON TV)
Dialogue: 0.0:48:47.31.0:48:48.31.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}{\i1}(MAN EXCLAIMS)
Dialogue: 0.0:48:48.31.0:48:51.81.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}{\i1}(EXPLOSIONS SOUNDING)
Dialogue: 0.0:48:51.81.0:48:55.53.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}NEWSREADER:\NMoroccan officials\Nare investigating suspects...
Dialogue: 0.0:48:55.53.0:48:58.03.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}{\i1}in the shooting of\Nan American tourist.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:58.03.0:49:01.95.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}Officials said the shooting\Ntook place...
Dialogue: 0.0:49:01.96.0:49:05.33.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}(ANNOUNCER CHATTERING\NIN JAPANESE)
Dialogue: 0.0:49:07.21.0:49:08.71.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}(BOTH LAUGHING)
Dialogue: 0.0:49:11.58.0:49:12.58.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(345.432)}Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0.0:49:12.58.0:49:14.58.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Yeah. I'm just going\Nto get my bag.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:20.81.0:49:23.48.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}The cops came again?
Dialogue: 0.0:49:23.48.0:49:26.81.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(137.432)}Yeah. They hadn't come\Nin nine months. But these were\Ndifferent cops.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:26.81.0:49:29.15.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}Did they come to ask\Nabout your mother's death?
Dialogue: 0.0:49:29.15.0:49:33.57.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}No. but they're probably\Ngoing to ask my dad\Nabout the same things.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:33.57.0:49:35.85.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}They're just not\Nconvinced. are they?
Dialogue: 0.0:49:42.36.0:49:45.86.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Believe it or not.\NI liked one of the cops.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:47.37.0:49:48.67.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(449.432)}Idiot.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:49.17.0:49:50.67.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(345.432)}Did you put on\Nsome panties?
Dialogue: 0.0:49:55.71.0:49:56.71.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}(BOTH LAUGHING)
Dialogue: 0.0:49:56.71.0:49:59.68.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}(CHATTERING IN JAPANESE)
Dialogue: 0.0:50:48.73.0:50:54.15.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}{\i1}(PEOPLE CHATTERING OVER RADIO)
Dialogue: 0.0:50:54.15.0:50:56.15.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}ALARID: (IN ARABIC)\NAre you sure\Nit was here?
Dialogue: 0.0:50:56.15.0:50:58.65.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}OLD MAN:\NAn American stopped me.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:58.66.0:51:03.09.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I was scared.\NHe was covered in blood.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:04.58.0:51:06.08.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Where was the bus stopped?
Dialogue: 0.0:51:06.08.0:51:07.83.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(384.432)}Over there.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:08.33.0:51:10.67.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}MAN ON RADIO:\NCaptain Alarid...\NCaptain Alarid.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:10.67.0:51:11.67.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}(RESPONDS IN ARABIC)
Dialogue: 0.0:51:11.67.0:51:13.03.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}I found cartridges.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:19.13.0:51:22.10.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(345.432)}We found four.\NHere's one.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:29.94.0:51:31.44.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Did you search all over?
Dialogue: 0.0:51:31.72.0:51:33.02.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}Yes. the whole mountain.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:52.16.0:51:54.66.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}They're from around here.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:54.66.0:51:56.66.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}Find out who has\Na .270 caliber rifle.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:12.43.0:52:13.76.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}(WOMAN SPEAKING ARABIC)
Dialogue: 0.0:52:21.82.0:52:24.02.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}(CAR DOORS SLAMMING)
Dialogue: 0.0:52:24.02.0:52:25.02.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(332.432)}ALARID:\NHassan Ibrahim?
Dialogue: 0.0:52:25.03.0:52:26.54.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.408)}Yes.\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hDrop your weapon.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:26.53.0:52:27.74.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I don't have a weapon.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:27.74.0:52:29.03.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(371.432)}Drop it now.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:29.03.0:52:29.91.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}I told you to drop\Nyour weapon.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:29.91.0:52:31.91.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}This is just my knife.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:32.42.0:52:33.43.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}Get on the ground.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:33.42.0:52:34.42.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}What did we do?
Dialogue: 0.0:52:34.42.0:52:36.42.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}Get down\Non the ground...\Nface down.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:38.34.0:52:40.34.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.432)}ALARID:\NDon't look at me.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:40.84.0:52:42.01.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}What did we do?
Dialogue: 0.0:52:42.01.0:52:43.71.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}(SHOUTING IN ARABIC)
Dialogue: 0.0:52:47.43.0:52:51.13.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}ABDULLAH:\NTake these skins to Najib.\Nsee if he wants to buy them.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:08.15.0:53:11.40.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.432)}Why did you shoot\Nat the bus?
Dialogue: 0.0:53:11.40.0:53:12.90.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}(SOBBING)
Dialogue: 0.0:53:13.41.0:53:15.91.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I didn't shoot at anyone.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:16.91.0:53:18.41.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(410.432)}Then who?
Dialogue: 0.0:53:25.75.0:53:27.25.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}It wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:30.34.0:53:31.59.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(HASSAN CRYING)
Dialogue: 0.0:53:31.59.0:53:34.23.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}That was your rifle.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:37.23.0:53:39.23.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I sold it yesterday.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:40.07.0:53:41.77.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}Who did you sell it to?
Dialogue: 0.0:54:09.96.0:54:11.46.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}(GREETING IN ARABIC)
Dialogue: 0.0:54:11.46.0:54:14.13.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}Do you know where\NAbdullah Adboum lives?
Dialogue: 0.0:54:15.14.0:54:16.86.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(423.432)}Yes.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:16.85.0:54:19.39.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}You have to go\Nover those mountains.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:23.89.0:54:25.89.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(358.432)}Who lives\Nin this area?
Dialogue: 0.0:54:25.90.0:54:29.04.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}We live here with our mother.\NAbdullah lives\Non the other side.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:32.62.0:54:37.82.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}If you're lying.\NI'm going to come back\Nand cut your balls off.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:37.82.0:54:40.21.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}You can come back\Nanytime you like.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:49.64.0:54:51.56.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Don't walk\Nbetween the graves.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:14.36.0:55:15.83.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}AHMED: Papa... Papa...
Dialogue: 0.0:55:15.83.0:55:16.83.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}What happened?
Dialogue: 0.0:55:16.83.0:55:19.33.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}The police...\Nthey're looking for you.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:19.33.0:55:20.75.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}Me? Why?
Dialogue: 0.0:55:20.75.0:55:22.92.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}No. not for you...\Nthey're looking for us.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:22.92.0:55:25.34.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Looking for you?\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0.0:55:25.34.0:55:27.51.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Because of the tourist.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:27.51.0:55:28.67.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.432)}What tourist?
Dialogue: 0.0:55:28.68.0:55:30.69.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}The American...\NYussef killed her.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:30.68.0:55:31.76.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}Liar. we both did.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:32.26.0:55:33.60.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0.0:55:33.60.0:55:35.71.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Yussef started shooting\Nat the cars...
Dialogue: 0.0:55:35.72.0:55:37.03.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}because Hassan said\Nthat the bullet could go far.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:37.02.0:55:39.18.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}Liar. you started\Nshooting at the cars.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:39.19.0:55:40.36.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}But you killed her.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:40.35.0:55:41.52.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0.0:55:41.52.0:55:44.52.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}Yussef killed the American\Nand he spies on\NZohra naked...
Dialogue: 0.0:55:44.52.0:55:46.73.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}and Zohra lets him\Nwatch her.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:46.73.0:55:48.53.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}ZOHRA: That's garbage.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:48.53.0:55:52.20.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}It's not garbage.\NShe's a street girl\Nand he spies on her.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:52.20.0:55:55.20.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}(BOTH CHATTERING ANGRILY\NIN ARABIC)
Dialogue: 0.0:55:55.20.0:55:56.20.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}(HORN HONKING)
Dialogue: 0.0:55:56.20.0:55:59.12.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}(PEOPLE CHEERING)
Dialogue: 0.0:55:59.12.0:56:01.04.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(332.432)}(IN SPANISH)\NTime to drink!
Dialogue: 0.0:56:02.63.0:56:06.64.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}(BAND PLAYING LIVELY MUSIC)
Dialogue: 0.0:56:12.84.0:56:15.60.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}{\i1}(PLAYING SLOW BLUES SONG)
Dialogue: 0.0:56:28.57.0:56:33.10.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.144)}(IN SPANISH)\NThis song is dedicated\Nfrom Luis to Patricia...
Dialogue: 0.0:56:33.11.0:56:35.70.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}the most beautiful bride\Nin the world.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:41.41.0:56:45.42.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}{\i1}(SINGING IN SPANISH)
Dialogue: 0.0:56:56.55.0:56:58.72.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}(SINGING ALONG)
Dialogue: 0.0:57:08.78.0:57:14.07.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}I think Aunt Amelia\Nhas to dance.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:15.40.0:57:19.98.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}(ALL CHATTERING IN SPANISH)
Dialogue: 0.0:57:35.00.0:57:36.67.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}{\i1}(PLAYING UPBEAT SPANISH MUSIC)
Dialogue: 0.0:58:02.45.0:58:06.12.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}Amelia. can I have\Nthis dance?
Dialogue: 0.0:58:06.12.0:58:08.38.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I don't think your wife\Nwould like that.
Dialogue: 0.0:58:08.37.0:58:13.45.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}Ohh. she passed away\N10 years ago.\NCome on Amelia.
Dialogue: 0.0:58:13.46.0:58:16.47.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}(CHATTERING IN SPANISH)
Dialogue: 0.0:58:23.22.0:58:27.36.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(137.432)}(PEOPLE CHATTERING IN SPANISH)
Dialogue: 0.0:58:32.19.0:58:36.90.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}{\i1}(LIVELY SPANISH MUSIC PLAYING)
Dialogue: 0.0:58:47.71.0:58:52.33.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}{\i1}(ROMANTIC SPANISH\NBALLAD PLAYING)
