Dialogue: 0.1:00:45.53.1:00:47.54.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}(ALL CHEERING)
Dialogue: 0.1:00:47.53.1:00:49.86.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(345.432)}{\i1}(COUNTING SONG\NIN SPANISH)
Dialogue: 0.1:00:49.86.1:00:52.58.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}{\i1}(NORTENO MUSIC PLAYING)
Dialogue: 0.1:00:59.42.1:01:03.42.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Let's go dance... You have\Nsomething white on your face.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:03.43.1:01:05.44.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}Don't get excited.\Nit's only cake.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:18.56.1:01:20.56.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}{\i1}ANNOUNCER ON RADIO:\N(IN ARABIC) Today.\Nnear Tazarine.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:20.56.1:01:22.48.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}{\i1}there was an incident.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:22.48.1:01:24.23.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}{\i1}An American was shot.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:24.23.1:01:29.20.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}Authorities say\Nit could have been a robbery.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:29.20.1:01:32.90.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}But. the American government\Nwas quick to suggest\Na terrorist link.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:32.91.1:01:35.22.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}{\i1}Minister Hassan Hazal\Nhas said...
Dialogue: 0.1:01:35.54.1:01:39.99.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}{\i1}that terrorist cells\Nhave been eradicated\Nin our country...
Dialogue: 0.1:01:40.00.1:01:43.09.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}{\i1}and one act\Nof vulgar banditry...
Dialogue: 0.1:01:43.08.1:01:48.09.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}{\i1}followed by\Nsuperficial evaluations\Nthe U.S. places on it...
Dialogue: 0.1:01:48.09.1:01:50.42.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}{\i1}cannot ruin our image\Nor the economy.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:51.59.1:01:52.47.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}(SUSAN GRUNTING)
Dialogue: 0.1:01:52.48.1:01:54.77.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}(MEN CHATTERING IN ARABIC)
Dialogue: 0.1:01:57.15.1:01:58.98.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}SUSAN: I want to\Ncall the kids.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:00.35.1:02:02.35.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}Richard. I want to\Ntalk to the kids.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:02.35.1:02:04.10.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}We can't move you\Nright now.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:04.35.1:02:07.07.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.408)}We'll call them later.\N\h\hI want to talk to the kids.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:08.49.1:02:09.99.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}I got to talk to them.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:22.87.1:02:24.87.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}SUSAN: I got to\Ntalk to the kids.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:27.76.1:02:29.76.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}(SOBBING)
Dialogue: 0.1:02:51.62.1:02:53.37.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(SPEAKING SOFTLY IN ARABIC)
Dialogue: 0.1:03:43.79.1:03:47.52.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(PRAYING IN ARABIC)
Dialogue: 0.1:03:55.05.1:03:59.05.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(IN FRENCH) You have to\Nturn on the air-conditioning.\Nmy husband is ill.
Dialogue: 0.1:03:59.05.1:04:02.02.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}(IN FRENCH)\NNo air-conditioning.\Nno gasoline near. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:02.02.1:04:05.61.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}Please. it's too hot.\NWe can get dehydrated.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:05.61.1:04:06.52.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}(IN ENGLISH)\NWhat did he say?
Dialogue: 0.1:04:06.53.1:04:08.37.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}He says we can't turn on\Nthe air-conditioning
Dialogue: 0.1:04:08.78.1:04:11.31.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}because it uses the gas.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:11.31.1:04:13.61.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}Oh. fuck that. Come on.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:15.87.1:04:17.37.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(345.432)}Fuck you.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:22.63.1:04:23.97.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Tom. where are you going?
Dialogue: 0.1:04:24.38.1:04:26.88.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}Get back.\NWait there. Get back.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:32.55.1:04:35.05.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.408)}TOM: Look. we're leaving.\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\hRICHARD:\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\hYou're not leaving us.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:35.05.1:04:37.56.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}There's old people here.\NThe heat is really getting...
Dialogue: 0.1:04:37.56.1:04:38.51.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}Wait for the ambulance.\Nand then you can leave.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:38.51.1:04:40.51.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}There's a man in the bus\Nwho almost fainted.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:40.51.1:04:42.84.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}and there's a woman who\Nneeds to get back in time\Nto take her medication.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:42.85.1:04:45.36.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(137.408)}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hWALTER: We can't\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hleave him here.\NTOM: Well. let him come. then.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:45.35.1:04:46.85.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}His wife's in no\Ncondition to travel.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:47.35.1:04:48.85.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}There's people\Nin no condition\Nto be kept waiting.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:48.85.1:04:50.60.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Can't you see that?
Dialogue: 0.1:04:50.60.1:04:53.60.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Please wait. The ambulance\Nis gonna be here\Nany minute. right?
Dialogue: 0.1:04:53.61.1:04:55.12.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}It's gonna be\Nhere any minute.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:55.11.1:04:58.69.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}So I'm asking you all\Nto please wait.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:01.11.1:05:02.91.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(345.432)}30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:02.92.1:05:04.84.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}We're giving you\N30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:22.47.1:05:23.47.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(358.432)}(LAUGHING)
Dialogue: 0.1:05:32.31.1:05:33.81.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}(GIRLS LAUGHING)
Dialogue: 0.1:05:45.66.1:05:47.04.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(358.432)}Who are they?
Dialogue: 0.1:05:48.04.1:05:49.21.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}My cousins.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:49.21.1:05:50.66.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Is he deaf-mute\Nlike us?
Dialogue: 0.1:05:50.66.1:05:52.66.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}No. but he\Nunderstands some.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:58.84.1:06:01.39.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(SPEAKING SLOWLY)\NWhat is your name?
Dialogue: 0.1:06:10.43.1:06:11.93.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Chieko.
Dialogue: 0.1:06:12.43.1:06:15.57.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}My name's Haruki.
Dialogue: 0.1:06:32.59.1:06:34.59.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}It's whisky.
Dialogue: 0.1:06:37.79.1:06:42.55.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(BOYS CHATTERING IN JAPANESE)
Dialogue: 0.1:06:49.47.1:06:52.89.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Do the cops\Ncome around here?
Dialogue: 0.1:06:54.19.1:06:55.69.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}Sometimes.
