Dialogue: 0.1:14:34.43.1:14:36.59.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(332.432)}(IN JAPANESE)\NWelcome home...\Nmay I help you?
Dialogue: 0.1:14:47.27.1:14:50.78.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(371.432)}Are you sure\Nyou want him\Nto come now?
Dialogue: 0.1:15:06.49.1:15:10.54.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}Is this Detective Mamiya?
Dialogue: 0.1:15:10.55.1:15:14.98.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}The deaf-mute girl\Nyou met this afternoon\Nasked me to call.
Dialogue: 0.1:15:14.97.1:15:17.38.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(410.432)}Yes. her.
Dialogue: 0.1:15:17.39.1:15:23.85.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}She says she\Nneeds to talk to you.\Nalone... about her father.
Dialogue: 0.1:15:25.56.1:15:28.18.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}ABDULLAH: (IN ARABIC)\NWhy did you do this?
Dialogue: 0.1:15:28.18.1:15:29.68.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}Why did you do this?
Dialogue: 0.1:15:32.65.1:15:34.15.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}Answer me. damn it!
Dialogue: 0.1:15:35.65.1:15:37.40.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}We were testing the rifle.
Dialogue: 0.1:15:38.91.1:15:40.91.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(332.432)}Are you idiots?
Dialogue: 0.1:15:40.91.1:15:42.58.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}You killed a woman.
Dialogue: 0.1:15:44.53.1:15:46.75.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(384.432)}And you....
Dialogue: 0.1:15:46.75.1:15:49.45.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}You got naked\Nso your brother could watch?
Dialogue: 0.1:15:51.25.1:15:54.29.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Zohra got naked lots of times\Nso Yussef could watch her.
Dialogue: 0.1:15:54.29.1:15:55.87.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}Is it true or not?
Dialogue: 0.1:16:00.18.1:16:01.93.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}Is it true or not?
Dialogue: 0.1:16:17.11.1:16:19.48.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}Why did you do this to us?
Dialogue: 0.1:16:21.40.1:16:22.73.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}Where's the rifle?
Dialogue: 0.1:16:24.70.1:16:26.65.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Where's the rifle?
Dialogue: 0.1:16:26.66.1:16:28.67.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I told you.\Na hunter gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0.1:16:29.16.1:16:30.57.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}What hunter?
Dialogue: 0.1:16:32.54.1:16:39.05.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}A Japanese hunter...\Ngave it to me.
Dialogue: 0.1:16:39.55.1:16:44.09.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}I've got a picture.\NShe can get it.
Dialogue: 0.1:16:44.09.1:16:45.59.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}POLICEMAN: Go get it.
Dialogue: 0.1:16:57.60.1:16:58.60.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}(CRYING)
Dialogue: 0.1:17:09.20.1:17:13.67.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}He's holding the rifle\Nhe gave me.
Dialogue: 0.1:17:39.70.1:17:41.04.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}We're going to Najib's house.
Dialogue: 0.1:17:41.03.1:17:44.32.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}If the cops come.\Ntell them we went south.
Dialogue: 0.1:17:51.16.1:17:53.07.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}{\i1}(CHATTER OVER POLICE RADIO)
Dialogue: 0.1:18:03.09.1:18:05.43.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}This Abdullah doesn't live\Nin the area you told us.
Dialogue: 0.1:18:05.42.1:18:07.92.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Are you playing with us?
Dialogue: 0.1:18:07.92.1:18:09.92.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}HASSAN'S WIFE: He lives\Nin the area he told you.
Dialogue: 0.1:18:09.93.1:18:12.44.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}He lives there?
Dialogue: 0.1:18:12.43.1:18:14.93.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}You're going to take us.
Dialogue: 0.1:18:17.93.1:18:20.43.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(CHATTERING IN ARABIC)
Dialogue: 0.1:18:25.44.1:18:26.94.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}{\i1}(ORDERS IN ARABIC)
Dialogue: 0.1:18:39.12.1:18:40.62.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}{\i1}(CHATTERING ON RADIO)
Dialogue: 0.1:18:48.26.1:18:52.55.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}(SPEAKING ARABIC)
Dialogue: 0.1:18:54.30.1:18:55.97.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}They're over there.
Dialogue: 0.1:18:59.14.1:19:01.03.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}The police. the police.
Dialogue: 0.1:19:02.03.1:19:03.31.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}Run... run.
