Dialogue: 0.1:22:36.61.1:22:38.61.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}From a wedding.
Dialogue: 0.1:22:40.11.1:22:41.28.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(332.432)}Where you from?
Dialogue: 0.1:22:41.28.1:22:43.28.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}From Valle\Nde Guadalupe.
Dialogue: 0.1:22:45.78.1:22:48.17.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Valle de Guadalupe.
Dialogue: 0.1:22:48.67.1:22:49.95.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Where you headed today?
Dialogue: 0.1:22:49.96.1:22:51.77.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}To San Diego. We're going...
Dialogue: 0.1:22:51.76.1:22:53.54.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}I'm taking them.
Dialogue: 0.1:22:56.29.1:22:58.21.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.408)}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hWho are they?\NHer nephews.
Dialogue: 0.1:22:58.21.1:23:00.43.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}Her nephews.\NThey don't look\Nlike you. ma'am.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:00.80.1:23:03.68.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}No. no. no. no.\NI'm in charge of them.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:04.69.1:23:06.52.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.408)}Do you have their passports?\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hYes.
