Dialogue: 0.1:25:54.76.1:25:56.26.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}Hey there. sweetie.
Dialogue: 0.1:25:56.26.1:25:59.14.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}Tell me. is this\Nlady here your auntie?
Dialogue: 0.1:25:59.14.1:26:00.81.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}No. she's not my auntie.
Dialogue: 0.1:26:02.76.1:26:04.15.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}She's in charge.
Dialogue: 0.1:26:04.15.1:26:06.15.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.408)}Are you drunk. sir?\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\hMe?
