Dialogue: 0.1:26:08.65.1:26:10.52.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}Sir. I'm gonna ask you\Nto step out the vehicle.
Dialogue: 0.1:26:10.52.1:26:13.77.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.408)}Why?\N\hI need you to step\N\hout the vehicle now.
Dialogue: 0.1:26:13.78.1:26:15.67.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}I need you to step\Nout the vehicle now!
