Dialogue: 0.1:26:18.00.1:26:20.87.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}I'm telling you\Nthat you will\Nstep out the vehicle!
Dialogue: 0.1:26:20.87.1:26:23.01.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(345.432)}Don't make me\Nask you again!
