Dialogue: 0.1:31:06.48.1:31:08.99.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}Yes. The third of five.
Dialogue: 0.1:31:12.32.1:31:13.82.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.432)}Do you have kids?
Dialogue: 0.1:31:13.83.1:31:15.34.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.1:31:38.10.1:31:39.27.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(358.432)}Just two?
