Dialogue: 0.1:31:43.44.1:31:44.94.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}You should have more.
Dialogue: 0.1:31:56.53.1:31:59.20.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}What about you?\NHow many wives you have?
Dialogue: 0.1:32:00.20.1:32:02.01.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}I can only afford one.
Dialogue: 0.1:32:15.72.1:32:17.30.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}Come on!\NFind another ambulance!\NDo something!
