Dialogue: 0.1:32:19.52.1:32:21.47.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}They just told me\Nthe ambulance isn't coming.
Dialogue: 0.1:32:21.98.1:32:24.31.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}And you know we don't\Nhave another ambulance.
Dialogue: 0.1:32:26.31.1:32:28.15.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}There isn't\Nanother ambulance.
Dialogue: 0.1:32:28.15.1:32:30.20.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}What do you mean.\Nthere's no other ambulance?\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0.1:32:30.20.1:32:34.15.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Fucking move!\NFucking find me an ambulance!\NFind me an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0.1:32:34.16.1:32:36.17.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}(IN ARABIC) He wants to know\Nhow he will get his wife\Nout of here.
Dialogue: 0.1:32:36.16.1:32:39.46.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}Tell him\Nthey said his embassy\Nwill deal with it.
Dialogue: 0.1:32:39.91.1:32:40.91.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}Your embassy\Nwill deal with it.
Dialogue: 0.1:32:40.91.1:32:42.41.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.432)}What can\Nmy embassy do?
Dialogue: 0.1:32:42.41.1:32:43.41.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}This is your fucked-up\Ncountry!
Dialogue: 0.1:32:43.41.1:32:45.22.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}It's your responsibility!\NYou do something!
Dialogue: 0.1:32:45.22.1:32:48.17.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(IN ARABIC) The Americans\Nstopped the ambulance.
Dialogue: 0.1:32:48.17.1:32:50.84.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}They want to\Nsend a helicopter.\Nbut there are problems.
Dialogue: 0.1:32:50.84.1:32:53.14.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}He says it's your embassy\Nwho stopped the ambulance
Dialogue: 0.1:32:53.14.1:32:55.01.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}and they will\Nsend a helicopter.
Dialogue: 0.1:32:55.01.1:32:59.06.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}Now I'm supposed to wait\Nfor a helicopter?\NFucking do something!
Dialogue: 0.1:32:59.06.1:33:00.93.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}Fuck you! Fuck you!
Dialogue: 0.1:33:05.15.1:33:06.57.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.408)}How's your wife?\N\h\h\hWe can't stay\N\h\h\hhere any longer.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:06.57.1:33:08.44.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.408)}Stay away from me.\N\hIt's gonna get dark soon.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:08.44.1:33:11.32.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}People are not feeling\Nwell. It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:11.33.1:33:13.12.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}Don't you push me!
Dialogue: 0.1:33:13.11.1:33:15.03.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}Fuck that! We're leaving!
Dialogue: 0.1:33:16.75.1:33:19.58.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.432)}Shut up! Shut up!\NShut up! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0.1:33:19.58.1:33:21.37.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}Take it easy!
Dialogue: 0.1:33:21.37.1:33:23.54.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.408)}\h\h\h\hShut up! Shut up!\NCalm down. Come here.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:24.54.1:33:26.34.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.408)}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hGet off me!\NCalm down!
Dialogue: 0.1:33:26.84.1:33:28.34.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(345.432)}If you leave.\NI'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:28.34.1:33:30.09.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(345.432)}I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:30.09.1:33:31.88.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}Come with us.\NCome with us.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:32.38.1:33:33.63.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(397.432)}Are you\Nall right?
Dialogue: 0.1:33:35.43.1:33:37.43.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}RICHARD:\NNo. we need help now.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:37.44.1:33:38.73.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}We need help now.\NDo you understand?
Dialogue: 0.1:33:38.72.1:33:40.64.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}MARK: I'm doing\Neverything I can do.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:40.64.1:33:42.69.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}I've got the State Department\Non the other line right now.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:42.69.1:33:44.44.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}They're doing\Neverything they can do.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:44.44.1:33:46.44.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}Due to some\Npolitical problems\Nthat are being resolved...
Dialogue: 0.1:33:46.44.1:33:48.70.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}I don't give a shit about\Npolitical problems.\NI need help now.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:48.70.1:33:50.70.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}Everybody is doing\Neverything they can.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:51.20.1:33:53.15.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}Okay? I don't know\Nwhat else I can do.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:53.15.1:33:55.15.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}It's all over the news.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:55.15.1:33:59.16.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}Everybody is paying attention\Nand doing everything\Nthat they can.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:59.16.1:34:00.29.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}Richard...
Dialogue: 0.1:34:13.09.1:34:17.67.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}Stop! Stop! Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0.1:34:51.84.1:34:53.34.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}(DOORBELL RINGING)
Dialogue: 0.1:35:06.89.1:35:08.27.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}(DOORBELL RINGING)
Dialogue: 0.1:35:10.73.1:35:12.23.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(358.432)}(IN JAPANESE)\NGood evening.
Dialogue: 0.1:35:12.23.1:35:15.23.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}The doorman called to say\Nyou wanted to talk to me.
Dialogue: 0.1:35:15.23.1:35:16.73.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0.1:35:16.73.1:35:19.15.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}Could you speak slowly?
Dialogue: 0.1:35:21.16.1:35:22.17.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(397.432)}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0.1:35:23.49.1:35:27.16.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}(SLOWLY) What was it\Nyou wanted to tell me?
Dialogue: 0.1:35:37.42.1:35:39.42.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY)
Dialogue: 0.1:35:41.93.1:35:43.94.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}Do you have tea?
Dialogue: 0.1:36:15.38.1:36:18.88.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}{\i1}"My father had nothing to do\Nwith my mother's death."
Dialogue: 0.1:36:22.35.1:36:23.68.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(371.432)}What's this?
Dialogue: 0.1:36:43.57.1:36:49.33.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}When your mother\Njumped off the balcony.\Nyour father was asleep?
Dialogue: 0.1:37:39.46.1:37:40.96.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.432)}You saw her jump?
Dialogue: 0.1:37:50.27.1:37:52.61.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}You've already told\Nthe other officers?
Dialogue: 0.1:38:06.82.1:38:08.65.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(345.432)}What are you\Ntalking about?
Dialogue: 0.1:38:53.83.1:38:57.67.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}Does your father\Nstill hunt?
Dialogue: 0.1:39:14.11.1:39:19.04.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}There was an incident\Ninvolving a rifle\Nin your father's name.
Dialogue: 0.1:39:19.03.1:39:22.53.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}That's why we want\Nto talk to him.\NUnderstand?
Dialogue: 0.1:40:03.52.1:40:08.52.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Your father\Nisn't going to jail.
Dialogue: 0.1:40:08.53.1:40:10.04.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}We just need\Nto talk to him.
Dialogue: 0.1:40:18.92.1:40:20.42.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}I have to go.
Dialogue: 0.1:40:23.76.1:40:25.42.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I really have to go.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:33.36.1:41:35.16.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0.1:41:46.76.1:41:48.26.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0.1:41:57.18.1:41:58.47.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(332.432)}Please stop.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:00.22.1:42:03.97.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}No. this is wrong.\NYou're just a girl.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:10.65.1:42:13.57.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}Enough. stop it!
Dialogue: 0.1:42:32.89.1:42:35.89.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}(SOBBING)
Dialogue: 0.1:42:52.32.1:42:56.53.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(SOBBING WRETCHEDLY)
Dialogue: 0.1:42:57.75.1:42:59.29.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}(GUNS FIRING)
Dialogue: 0.1:43:00.66.1:43:02.16.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}(IN ARABIC)\NGive me that rifle.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:02.17.1:43:03.88.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}They're going to kill us.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:07.79.1:43:09.54.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}They're going to kill us.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:14.01.1:43:16.43.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}(BOTH CHATTERING IN ARABIC)
Dialogue: 0.1:43:22.52.1:43:23.30.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(332.432)}Ahmed!
Dialogue: 0.1:43:25.22.1:43:26.27.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}Ahmed!
Dialogue: 0.1:43:26.77.1:43:28.02.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(358.432)}Ahmed!
Dialogue: 0.1:43:28.03.1:43:28.90.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(345.432)}Ahmed!
Dialogue: 0.1:43:30.14.1:43:31.14.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}Ahmed!
Dialogue: 0.1:43:35.57.1:43:36.46.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Ahmed!
Dialogue: 0.1:43:38.04.1:43:39.04.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}Ahmed.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:43.32.1:43:45.32.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(EXCLAIMS IN ARABIC)
Dialogue: 0.1:43:46.33.1:43:47.83.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}(SOBBING)
Dialogue: 0.1:44:00.51.1:44:02.01.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(358.432)}(PANTING)
Dialogue: 0.1:44:15.77.1:44:21.44.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}YUSSEF: (IN ARABIC)\NI killed the American. I was\Nthe only one who shot at you.
Dialogue: 0.1:44:21.95.1:44:23.54.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}(OFFICER SHOUTING IN ARABIC)
Dialogue: 0.1:44:26.83.1:44:30.34.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}YUSSEF: They did\Nnothing... nothing.
Dialogue: 0.1:44:34.51.1:44:40.60.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Kill me.\Nbut save my brother.\Nhe did nothing... nothing.
Dialogue: 0.1:44:46.55.1:44:48.55.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}(PLEADING IN ARABIC)
Dialogue: 0.1:44:50.06.1:44:54.06.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}Save my brother...\Nhe did nothing.
Dialogue: 0.1:45:47.25.1:45:48.70.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}(IN ENGLISH)\NHelp!
Dialogue: 0.1:45:48.70.1:45:50.20.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}(SHOUTING IN SPANISH)
Dialogue: 0.1:45:50.70.1:45:52.28.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}(IN ENGLISH)\NHelp!
Dialogue: 0.1:45:53.17.1:45:55.87.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(358.432)}Help!
Dialogue: 0.1:46:02.76.1:46:03.60.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}Help!
Dialogue: 0.1:46:08.27.1:46:10.22.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}(WHIMPERING)
Dialogue: 0.1:46:25.45.1:46:27.95.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.432)}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0.1:46:28.46.1:46:31.97.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}Why are we hiding\Nif we didn't even\Ndo anything wrong?
Dialogue: 0.1:46:31.96.1:46:37.33.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Because they think\Nwe did something wrong. baby.
Dialogue: 0.1:46:37.33.1:46:40.83.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}That's not true.\NYou're bad.
Dialogue: 0.1:46:42.72.1:46:46.47.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}No. sweetie. No. I'm not.
Dialogue: 0.1:46:47.47.1:46:50.48.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I just did\Nsomething stupid.
Dialogue: 0.1:46:50.98.1:46:54.26.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(WHISPERING IN SPANISH)
Dialogue: 0.1:46:54.26.1:46:55.76.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(KISSING COMFORTINGLY)
Dialogue: 0.1:48:30.41.1:48:34.11.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Sweetie. I have\Nto go look for help.
Dialogue: 0.1:48:34.11.1:48:36.62.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Stay here and\Ndon't move. please.
Dialogue: 0.1:48:37.12.1:48:40.12.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}I'm not\Nstaying here alone.
Dialogue: 0.1:48:40.12.1:48:43.62.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Honey. you have\Nto take care\Nof Debbie. baby.
Dialogue: 0.1:48:45.13.1:48:46.64.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}I'm going with you.
Dialogue: 0.1:48:48.13.1:48:51.63.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I won't be long.\NI promise. Stay here.
Dialogue: 0.1:48:52.60.1:48:54.43.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Don't move. Okay?
Dialogue: 0.1:48:54.80.1:48:56.80.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I won't be long. baby.
Dialogue: 0.1:49:01.69.1:49:04.36.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}(MIKE SOBBING)
Dialogue: 0.1:49:28.42.1:49:30.75.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}(PANTING)
Dialogue: 0.1:49:45.74.1:49:46.75.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(384.432)}(SIGHS)
Dialogue: 0.1:49:56.75.1:49:58.11.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}(IN ENGLISH)\NDrink.
Dialogue: 0.1:50:17.02.1:50:19.52.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}(GASPING IN SURPRISE)
Dialogue: 0.1:50:20.44.1:50:22.19.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(SHOUTING IN TRIUMPH)
Dialogue: 0.1:50:22.19.1:50:27.61.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}(BEGGING FOR HELP\NIN SPANISH)
Dialogue: 0.1:50:51.97.1:50:56.56.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I have to go and get two kids\NI left behind in the desert.\NPlease?
Dialogue: 0.1:50:56.56.1:50:58.56.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(384.432)}(QUESTIONS\NIN SPANISH)
Dialogue: 0.1:50:59.06.1:51:00.48.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(IN ENGLISH)\NThey're Americans.
Dialogue: 0.1:51:00.48.1:51:03.68.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.408)}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hWhen did you cross?\NI didn't cross. I live here.
Dialogue: 0.1:51:03.68.1:51:07.43.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Please. please.\Nhelp me find those kids.
Dialogue: 0.1:51:07.43.1:51:09.15.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(384.432)}Stand here.\NDon't move.
Dialogue: 0.1:51:14.91.1:51:17.28.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}Attention. Dispatch.\NI think I got the suspect.
Dialogue: 0.1:51:21.62.1:51:23.34.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}{\i1}(CHATTERING OVER POLICE RADIO)
Dialogue: 0.1:51:27.09.1:51:29.54.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}Ma'am. you're under arrest.\NYou want to turn around
Dialogue: 0.1:51:29.54.1:51:32.37.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}and put your hands\Nbehind your head. please.
Dialogue: 0.1:51:32.71.1:51:35.43.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I live with those\Nkids. I swear!
Dialogue: 0.1:51:35.43.1:51:38.76.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.408)}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hTurn around.\NPlease. sir.\Nthose kids will die!
Dialogue: 0.1:51:39.27.1:51:40.28.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0.1:51:40.77.1:51:42.27.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(384.432)}(IMPLORING\NIN SPANISH)
Dialogue: 0.1:51:54.03.1:51:55.31.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Then we'll get\Nyou some water.
Dialogue: 0.1:51:55.32.1:51:58.38.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(345.432)}(IN SPANISH)\NThey're alone.
Dialogue: 0.1:52:00.32.1:52:03.99.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}(IN SPANISH)\NThey are children.\Nthey will die.
Dialogue: 0.1:52:03.99.1:52:07.13.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}OFFICER: (IN ENGLISH)\NYou're gonna take me\Nto them. okay?
Dialogue: 0.1:52:20.84.1:52:21.84.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}(INAUDIBLE)
Dialogue: 0.1:52:28.85.1:52:30.40.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}(CALLING TO KIDS\NIN SPANISH)
Dialogue: 0.1:52:38.16.1:52:39.74.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Ma'am. are you\Nwith them?
Dialogue: 0.1:53:13.53.1:53:15.03.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(345.432)}{\i1}SUSAN: Richard?
Dialogue: 0.1:53:20.40.1:53:21.40.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}What?
Dialogue: 0.1:53:23.40.1:53:27.41.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}If I die. you take care\Nof the kids.
Dialogue: 0.1:53:29.91.1:53:31.91.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}Especially Mike.\NHe really needs you.
Dialogue: 0.1:53:31.91.1:53:35.41.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}You're not gonna die.\NYou can't die.\NYou just can't.
Dialogue: 0.1:53:36.42.1:53:38.42.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.432)}Don't you ever\Nleave them again.
Dialogue: 0.1:53:41.00.1:53:43.00.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I will never leave them.
Dialogue: 0.1:53:53.68.1:53:54.68.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}I peed my pants.
Dialogue: 0.1:53:55.69.1:53:56.70.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}What?
Dialogue: 0.1:53:58.19.1:54:02.19.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}I couldn't hold it in\Nand I peed.
Dialogue: 0.1:54:11.92.1:54:13.92.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}I've got to pee again.
Dialogue: 0.1:54:20.09.1:54:22.09.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}Do you have\Na pan we could use?
Dialogue: 0.1:54:23.10.1:54:24.10.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(358.432)}A pan?
Dialogue: 0.1:54:30.69.1:54:33.05.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Could you give us\Na few moments alone?
Dialogue: 0.1:54:33.06.1:54:34.57.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Yeah. of course.
Dialogue: 0.1:54:47.74.1:54:49.57.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}There.
Dialogue: 0.1:54:49.57.1:54:50.54.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}Now sit.
Dialogue: 0.1:54:53.04.1:54:54.04.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(423.432)}I can't.
Dialogue: 0.1:54:59.55.1:55:02.05.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.432)}Yep. Yeah. I can.
Dialogue: 0.1:55:12.01.1:55:16.52.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(358.432)}(URINATING)
Dialogue: 0.1:55:32.53.1:55:33.53.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(358.432)}(CHUCKLES)
Dialogue: 0.1:55:43.26.1:55:46.26.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(371.432)}(SOBBING)
Dialogue: 0.1:56:02.11.1:56:04.15.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}Forgive me. my love.
Dialogue: 0.1:56:06.65.1:56:08.65.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}When Sammy died.
Dialogue: 0.1:56:10.65.1:56:12.15.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I didn't...
Dialogue: 0.1:56:18.24.1:56:19.24.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}I ran.
Dialogue: 0.1:56:27.75.1:56:29.25.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}I was scared.
Dialogue: 0.1:56:29.26.1:56:30.77.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}I was scared. too.
Dialogue: 0.1:56:32.76.1:56:34.09.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}It wasn't my fault.
Dialogue: 0.1:56:34.09.1:56:36.60.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.408)}It wasn't your fault.\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hIt wasn't my fault.
Dialogue: 0.1:56:36.60.1:56:37.43.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}It wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0.1:56:37.43.1:56:39.43.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}He wasn't breathing.
Dialogue: 0.1:56:39.93.1:56:41.43.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(332.432)}I couldn't...
Dialogue: 0.1:56:44.82.1:56:46.32.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I love you so much.
Dialogue: 0.1:56:56.50.1:56:58.50.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I'm forgetting his face.
Dialogue: 0.1:57:00.50.1:57:02.45.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}CLIFFORD ON PHONE:\NHello? Richard Jones?
Dialogue: 0.1:57:02.46.1:57:04.47.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}I'm very sorry about\Nwhat happened to your wife.
Dialogue: 0.1:57:04.46.1:57:06.46.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}but you can be sure\Nthat the culprits\Nwill be punished.
Dialogue: 0.1:57:06.71.1:57:08.38.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}{\i1}RICHARD: What the fuck is\Ntaking so long?
Dialogue: 0.1:57:08.38.1:57:10.38.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}Well. the Moroccan government\Nwouldn't let us\Nuse their airspace.
Dialogue: 0.1:57:10.38.1:57:12.88.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}They refused to acknowledge\Nthat this was\Nan act of terrorism.
Dialogue: 0.1:57:12.88.1:57:14.38.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}{\i1}What about the ambulance?
Dialogue: 0.1:57:14.88.1:57:16.47.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}Taking your safety\Ninto consideration. Mr. Jones.
Dialogue: 0.1:57:16.47.1:57:19.85.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}we didn't believe\Nit would be appropriate\Nto send a Moroccan ambulance.
Dialogue: 0.1:57:19.86.1:57:20.98.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}Stay put.\NWe settled the matter.
Dialogue: 0.1:57:21.47.1:57:22.86.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}A helicopter\Nshould arrive soon.
Dialogue: 0.1:57:22.86.1:57:24.14.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.408)}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h{\i1}How long?\NSoon.
Dialogue: 0.1:57:24.14.1:57:25.56.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(371.432)}{\i1}No! How long?
Dialogue: 0.1:57:32.24.1:57:35.25.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}KENJI: (IN JAPANESE)\NThere's no need to apologize.
Dialogue: 0.1:59:06.05.1:59:08.06.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(BIDDING FAREWELL\NIN JAPANESE)
Dialogue: 0.1:59:36.53.1:59:38.04.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(SHUFFLING PAPERS)
Dialogue: 0.1:59:39.53.1:59:41.41.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}It's a miracle\Nwe found those kids. ma'am.
Dialogue: 0.1:59:41.41.1:59:45.42.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I don't know how you\Ncould have left them alone\Nlike that out in the desert.
Dialogue: 0.1:59:46.92.1:59:48.92.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}How are they. sir?
Dialogue: 0.1:59:48.92.1:59:51.92.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.432)}That's none\Nof your business.
Dialogue: 0.1:59:51.93.1:59:55.94.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}You know how many\Nkids die every year\Ntrying to cross this border?
Dialogue: 0.1:59:59.43.2:00:02.93.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I raised these kids\Nsince they were born.
Dialogue: 0.2:00:02.94.2:00:06.45.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I take care of them\Nday and night.
Dialogue: 0.2:00:06.44.2:00:10.44.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I feed them breakfast\Nand lunch and dinner.
Dialogue: 0.2:00:10.44.2:00:13.45.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}I play with them.
Dialogue: 0.2:00:13.45.2:00:16.45.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Mike and Debbie\Nare like my own children.
Dialogue: 0.2:00:16.45.2:00:18.87.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}But they are not\Nyour children. ma'am.
Dialogue: 0.2:00:20.37.2:00:23.37.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}Plus. you've been working\Nin this country illegally.
Dialogue: 0.2:00:31.30.2:00:33.80.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}What about\Nmy nephew. Santiago?
Dialogue: 0.2:00:34.30.2:00:37.30.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}I don't have any\Ninformation on him.
Dialogue: 0.2:00:37.30.2:00:39.30.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}We located the father\Nin Morocco.
Dialogue: 0.2:00:39.31.2:00:42.32.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}He was very angry.\Nbut decided not\Nto press charges.
Dialogue: 0.2:00:43.31.2:00:44.81.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0.2:00:44.81.2:00:46.81.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}Nevertheless the government\Nof the United States
Dialogue: 0.2:00:46.81.2:00:49.31.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}has deemed that you are\Nseriously breaking the law.
Dialogue: 0.2:00:49.32.2:00:52.66.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}and is\Ndetermined to immediately\Nand definitively deport you.
Dialogue: 0.2:00:55.02.2:00:59.02.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Sir. I...\NI've been here for 16 years.
Dialogue: 0.2:01:00.53.2:01:05.03.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I--I have my things here.\NI rent a house.
Dialogue: 0.2:01:05.03.2:01:07.53.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I made a life here. sir.
Dialogue: 0.2:01:07.53.2:01:10.03.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}You should have thought\Nabout that beforehand.
Dialogue: 0.2:01:16.34.2:01:19.21.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}I want to talk\Nto a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0.2:01:19.71.2:01:23.72.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}If you attempt\Nto take this to trial.\NI can assure you.
Dialogue: 0.2:01:23.72.2:01:25.72.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(332.432)}you'll only\Nbe prolonging\Nthe inevitable.
Dialogue: 0.2:01:27.72.2:01:30.22.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}I recommend you accept\Nvoluntary deportation.
Dialogue: 0.2:01:33.23.2:01:34.74.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}(SOBS)
Dialogue: 0.2:05:30.05.2:05:32.06.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}{\i1}FEMALE REPORTER:\NThe sources of the attack\Nare not yet known.
Dialogue: 0.2:05:32.05.2:05:37.27.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}But it is clear that Moroccan\Nand US government officials
Dialogue: 0.2:05:37.60.2:05:41.94.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}{\i1}are working quickly\Nto secure the area\Nfor all citizens.
Dialogue: 0.2:05:41.94.2:05:47.06.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}{\i1}Locals reported Susan Jones.\Nan American mother of two...
Dialogue: 0.2:05:47.06.2:05:49.86.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}Mr. Jones.\NI'm Ken Clifford.\Nthe US ambassador.
Dialogue: 0.2:06:08.13.2:06:09.58.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}CLIFFORD: We will\Nfind these people.
Dialogue: 0.2:06:09.59.2:06:11.35.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}Whoever they are.\Nwe will find them.
Dialogue: 0.2:06:11.34.2:06:14.14.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Thank you very much.\NThat's all I have to say now.
Dialogue: 0.2:06:38.25.2:06:39.61.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(345.432)}Mr. Jones?
Dialogue: 0.2:06:41.53.2:06:44.04.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}I'm going to have to\Noperate immediately.
Dialogue: 0.2:06:44.04.2:06:45.54.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}Is she gonna be\Nall right?
Dialogue: 0.2:06:46.04.2:06:47.54.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(345.432)}It's probable.
Dialogue: 0.2:06:47.54.2:06:49.54.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}We're gonna try\Nto save her arm.
Dialogue: 0.2:06:49.54.2:06:51.04.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}She's been\Nbleeding internally
Dialogue: 0.2:06:51.54.2:06:52.54.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}and there's\Nbeen some clotting.
Dialogue: 0.2:06:53.05.2:06:55.06.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.432)}so there's a high\Nrisk of gangrene.
Dialogue: 0.2:06:56.55.2:06:58.55.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}But is she\Ngonna be all right?
Dialogue: 0.2:07:01.39.2:07:02.85.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(332.432)}Excuse me. sir.
Dialogue: 0.2:07:13.37.2:07:14.88.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}{\i1}(RINGING)
Dialogue: 0.2:07:18.87.2:07:21.37.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.408)}{\i1}AMELIA: Yes?\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h{\r}Amelia?
Dialogue: 0.2:07:21.87.2:07:23.37.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}Yes. sir.
Dialogue: 0.2:07:23.88.2:07:25.38.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}Hi. how's everything?
Dialogue: 0.2:07:25.88.2:07:27.38.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}Everything is okay. sir.
Dialogue: 0.2:07:27.88.2:07:29.38.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}Mrs. Rachel told me.
Dialogue: 0.2:07:29.38.2:07:31.38.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}I am very sorry. sir.
Dialogue: 0.2:07:31.88.2:07:33.38.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}How's Mrs. Susan?
Dialogue: 0.2:07:33.39.2:07:34.90.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.432)}She's better now.
Dialogue: 0.2:07:34.89.2:07:37.39.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}They're going to\Nhave to operate. but...
Dialogue: 0.2:07:37.39.2:07:40.39.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}Look. Rachel's\Nflying in tonight.
Dialogue: 0.2:07:40.39.2:07:43.90.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}She's gonna find someone\Nto take care of the kids\Nso you can go.
Dialogue: 0.2:07:45.40.2:07:46.90.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}Thank you. sir. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0.2:07:46.90.2:07:48.40.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}I really appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0.2:07:50.90.2:07:53.91.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}So. look after them. okay?\NDon't tell them anything.
Dialogue: 0.2:07:53.91.2:07:56.41.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}No. no. no. Don't worry. sir.\NDon't worry.
Dialogue: 0.2:07:56.41.2:07:57.91.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(345.432)}Okay.
Dialogue: 0.2:07:57.91.2:08:00.91.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(267.432)}Put Mike on. please.
Dialogue: 0.2:08:00.91.2:08:03.41.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}Mike? Your dad is calling.
Dialogue: 0.2:08:08.42.2:08:10.92.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.408)}{\i1}Hi. Daddy.\N\h\h\h{\r}Hi. sweetie. How are you?
Dialogue: 0.2:08:10.92.2:08:14.84.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}Good. Dad. guess what?\NToday they brought\Nhermit crabs to class.
Dialogue: 0.2:08:15.34.2:08:16.84.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(345.432)}Oh. really?
Dialogue: 0.2:08:17.35.2:08:19.35.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}I held one in my hands.\NIt bit me.
Dialogue: 0.2:08:19.35.2:08:21.85.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}It really\Ndidn't bleed. but...
Dialogue: 0.2:08:21.85.2:08:22.85.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}(SNIFFING)
Dialogue: 0.2:08:22.85.2:08:24.85.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}Dad? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0.2:08:26.36.2:08:28.87.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}I'm okay.\NEverything's fine.
Dialogue: 0.2:08:28.86.2:08:30.36.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}Mariana wanted\Nto take one home.
Dialogue: 0.2:08:30.36.2:08:31.86.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}But the teacher\Ndidn't let her. She was...
Dialogue: 0.2:08:32.36.2:08:34.86.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}I felt sad for her 'cause\Nshe went to\Nthe principal's office.
Dialogue: 0.2:08:34.86.2:08:36.36.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}You know what she did?
Dialogue: 0.2:08:36.37.2:08:37.88.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}She started crying.
Dialogue: 0.2:08:37.87.2:08:41.37.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}{\i1}She was really crying.\NAnd the teacher\Nhad to send her
Dialogue: 0.2:08:41.37.2:08:45.62.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}to the principal's office\N'cause she was really crying.
Dialogue: 0.2:08:54.55.2:08:55.97.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}(ELEVATOR BELL DINGS)
Dialogue: 0.2:09:07.85.2:09:13.10.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}(IN JAPANESE)\NMr. Wataya. this officer\Nhas been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0.2:09:16.69.2:09:22.19.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}Good evening.\NI'm Lieutenant Mamiya.
Dialogue: 0.2:09:22.19.2:09:24.75.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(IN JAPANESE)\NGood evening.\Nhow can I help you?
Dialogue: 0.2:09:27.28.2:09:29.78.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}Sir. there was\Nan incident and...
Dialogue: 0.2:09:30.87.2:09:32.87.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(293.432)}I'm sorry to\Nbother you. but...
Dialogue: 0.2:09:33.37.2:09:36.87.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}do you own a .270 caliber\NWinchester M70 rifle?
Dialogue: 0.2:09:38.38.2:09:40.26.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(241.432)}Registration number...
Dialogue: 0.2:09:42.30.2:09:45.47.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(410.432)}UK-9023.
Dialogue: 0.2:09:45.97.2:09:49.97.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I don't remember the number.\Nbut I did have\Na rifle like that.
Dialogue: 0.2:09:49.97.2:09:52.97.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}Is it true\Nthat you gave that rifle\Nto a Mr. Hassan Ibrahim...
Dialogue: 0.2:09:52.98.2:09:54.99.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}who lives in Morocco?
Dialogue: 0.2:09:54.98.2:09:56.28.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(189.432)}Hassan Ibrahim?
Dialogue: 0.2:09:57.78.2:10:00.78.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}He says he was\Nyour guide in a hunt.
Dialogue: 0.2:10:00.78.2:10:02.90.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Hassan? Yes.\NI remember him well.
Dialogue: 0.2:10:02.90.2:10:08.71.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}He was a good guide and\Na very good man. I gave him\Nthe rifle in thanks.
Dialogue: 0.2:10:10.99.2:10:13.49.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Did anything happen?
Dialogue: 0.2:10:13.50.2:10:16.81.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(202.432)}That rifle was used\Nin an attempted murder...
Dialogue: 0.2:10:16.80.2:10:20.80.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}and the Moroccan police want\Nto confirm it's not\Noff the black market.
Dialogue: 0.2:10:20.80.2:10:23.80.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}No. I gave it to him.
Dialogue: 0.2:10:25.42.2:10:27.93.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}Is Hassan ok?
Dialogue: 0.2:10:29.40.2:10:31.41.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0.2:10:35.85.2:10:38.35.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}Am I legally involved?
Dialogue: 0.2:10:38.35.2:10:43.32.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(215.432)}Not for the moment.\Nbut can you come down\Nto the station tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0.2:10:43.33.2:10:45.34.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}I have\Na few questions.
Dialogue: 0.2:10:47.33.2:10:48.61.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}Can I leave now?
Dialogue: 0.2:10:49.62.2:10:51.13.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(358.432)}Good night.
Dialogue: 0.2:10:55.20.2:10:56.70.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(397.432)}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0.2:10:58.37.2:11:00.34.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(254.432)}I heard\Nfrom your daughter...
Dialogue: 0.2:11:01.34.2:11:03.34.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(332.432)}about your wife\Non the balcony.
Dialogue: 0.2:11:04.55.2:11:06.05.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(332.432)}I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0.2:11:06.68.2:11:08.30.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(228.432)}What balcony?
Dialogue: 0.2:11:09.80.2:11:13.97.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}About how\Nyour wife killed herself\Nby jumping off the balcony.
Dialogue: 0.2:11:21.98.2:11:26.78.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}My wife never\Njumped off a balcony.\NShe shot herself in the head.
Dialogue: 0.2:11:26.79.2:11:28.80.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}My daughter was\Nthe first to find her.
Dialogue: 0.2:11:30.79.2:11:33.57.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}I've explained it\Nto the police many times.
Dialogue: 0.2:11:35.58.2:11:39.08.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}Don't bother us\Nwith that anymore.
Dialogue: 0.2:11:39.08.2:11:42.00.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(163.432)}I'm very sorry sir. we won't\Nbother you anymore.
Dialogue: 0.2:11:42.00.2:11:43.00.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(371.432)}Good night.
Dialogue: 0.2:12:35.72.2:12:37.52.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(319.432)}Another shochu.
Dialogue: 0.2:13:08.09.2:13:09.55.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}(SPEAKING JAPANESE)
Dialogue: 0.2:13:10.06.2:13:11.57.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(280.432)}(SPEAKING JAPANESE)
Dialogue: 0.2:13:15.56.2:13:18.76.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(150.432)}{\i1}(IN JAPANESE) Susan Jones.\Nwho was wounded in a terrorist\Nattack in Morocco...
Dialogue: 0.2:13:18.76.2:13:23.07.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(176.432)}{\i1}was discharged from\Na Casablanca hospital\Nthis morning. local time.
